high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the sink that's on your right and face it.
Pick up the clear glass bottle that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk  to the toaster.
Open the cupboard above the toaster and put the bottle on the plate up there.
Pick up the plate and close the cupboard.
Walk back to the sink.
Put the plate with the bottle on it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a bottle on top of it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the closest glass bottle off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk over to the toaster, then look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet door and put the bottle on the plate inside.
Take the plate with the bottle on it out of the cabinet and close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the plate with the bottle on it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a bottle on it in the sink.
